query:
INSERT INTO
                leaf_aggregation_witness_jobs_fri (
                    l1_batch_number,
                    circuit_id,
                    status,
                    number_of_basic_circuits,
                    created_at,
                    updated_at
                )
            VALUES
                ($1, $2, 'waiting_for_proofs', 2, NOW(), NOW()) ON CONFLICT (l1_batch_number, circuit_id) DO
            UPDATE
            SET
                status = $3
